{"tid":2404193,"cid":30,"subCid":0,"title":"入嚟講兩句 好想時間快啲過(13)","createTime":"2021-02-11T14:31:41.000Z","updateTime":"2021-02-11T15:22:51.000Z","uid":388586,"like":0,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":3,"replies":[{"pid":"af62a28ddf71f6328523eda3bbfe8e9c5e39c219","tid":2404193,"uid":388586,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-02-11T14:31:41.000Z","msg":"(樓主行開咗遲遲唔開post<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/aura.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />所以由我嚟開！)<br />\n<br />\n依個post係俾失眠 失戀 想吐苦水 傾心事嘅人圍爐<br />\n<br />\n多謝上幾個post陪過我 俾過意見我嘅咁多位！<img src=\"/assets/faces/mouse/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n依個post 除咗係圍爐取暖 <br />\n<br />\n大家都可以入嚟吹下水 發下癲<br />\n分享一下去嗰邊 做咗啲乜嘢 <br />\n除咗擺低自己心事 都可以散播正能量<img src=\"/assets/faces/mouse/tea.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n有咩開心野想分享都可以返嚟㗎<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n樓豬！Kai子！窮！雪！多疑絲！ 大粒麥！跟我來巴！<br />\nCylmomt！辣油！可能巴！塵埃！Gary！<br />\n戒賭！宋文德！唔好玩絲！擱淺絲！成熟巴！<br />\n旅行巴！因緣巴！洞洞丸！別姫！冇我嘅事絲！獵豹絲！<br />\n仲有好多位！<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n嗚 越來越多人唔係記得好清楚<br />\n如果你成日留名 但係我唔記得加你個名嘅話對唔住<img src=\"/assets/faces/mouse/please.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/mouse/please.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"4271da016f9b648b2af59b0180f5b45fb55e50eb","tid":2404193,"uid":325588,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2021-02-11T14:33:03.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"81a4ef75c6d64bb44419e6d1f59ca02a74fc0960","tid":2404193,"uid":388586,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"4271da016f9b648b2af59b0180f5b45fb55e50eb","tid":2404193,"uid":325588,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2021-02-11T14:33:03.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2021-02-11T14:34:06.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"1089be668d7337ea